<div class='communityQuestionAndAnswer'>
<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1299765-i-want-to-share-my-thoughts-about-this">I want to share my thoughts about this book. No one can say &quot;Nazis were right&quot; or &quot;Jews had to die&quot;. He is right about anything that he said but this book is not good for kids. I born in Germany, and I am a teacher in USA. When we read this book at school kids had questions in their head. These questions were about me. The students start asking &quot;did you kill a Jew ?&quot;, &quot;are you Nazi ?&quot; because they were just 13.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1299765'><a id="like_count_community_question_1299765" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1299765?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">10 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F1617.Night">like</a></span>

